description: User-friendly ultra-high resolution digital imaging system with USB 3.0 connection and DICOM compatibility, facilitated by TD-10 digital camera and EyeCAM image & video archiving software. The epitome of digital imaging with ultra-high quality and ease of use is the Takagi’s Eye Cam Digital Camera. Furthermore, this state-of-the-art system stresses usability, additionally, it also produces images and videos of superior quality. The Eye Cam Camera is a multifunctional and essential instrument that improves professional imaging requirements, whether it is used for industrial, medical, or research purposes.
